  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When a creature with hardness takes damage, subtract its hardness from the damage. Only damage in excess of its hardness is subtracted from its hit points. A creature with hardness doesn&rsquo;t further reduce damage from energy attacks, ranged attacks, or other types of attacks as objects typically do. Adamantine weapons bypass hardness of 20 or less.</p>&nbsp;<p><em>Format</em>: hardness 10</p><p><em>Location</em>: Defensive Abilities.</p>",
